    PetrolGeneratorCoupledModel
    The class PetrolGeneratorCoupledModel defines a simple coupled model used to assemble the models defined for the Petrol Generator in order to execute unit tests on the Petrol Generator simulator.

    The class PetrolGeneratorElectricityModel defines a simulation model for the electricity production of the PetrolGenerator.

    The enumeration GeneratorState describes the operation states of the Petrol Generator.

    The class PetrolGeneratorElectricityReport implements the simulation report for the PetrolGeneratorElectricityModel.

    The class PetrolGeneratorUnitTesterModel defines a model that is used to test the models defining the PetrolGenerator simulator.

    The class RunPetrolGeneratorUnitarySimulation creates a simulator for the PetrolGenerator and then runs a typical simulation.
